						 <p>Noting a reversion from an edit made by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kobon" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2884200&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1489241129" alt="Kobon" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2884200)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kobon" >Kobon</a></span>, who has made the following edit: Changed &quot;Sugarcomb Industries&quot; to &quot;Sugarcomb Confectionery&quot;.</p> <p>Since this is an edit in content, note that one requires the permission of the article's author. Non-authors for non-collab articles should only edit errors in spelling, grammar or punctuation. Anything beyond that should require author's approval.</p> 
