				<wikidot:authorName>azzleflux</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1444699</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I specified osseus tissue because it wasn't supposed to be just that specific tissue; I had a different colored nymph converting yellow marrow, so just saying &quot;skeletal&quot; tissue wouldn't make sense. Gastrointestinal and cardiovascular are supposed to be all-inclusive within their respective systems.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
